text: "Universe" is a 1997 song by Australian pop duo Savage Garden and is the fifth single from their self-titled debut studio album. It went to number 25 in New Zealand and number 26 in Australia. == Track listing == # "Universe" – 4:21 # "Love Can Move You" – 4:47 # "This Side of Me" (short version) – 3:51 # "Universe" (Future of Earthly Delites Mix) – 4:38 Category:1997 songs Category:Savage Garden songs
title: Universe (Savage Garden song)
